184
00:11:57.375 --> 00:12:04.208
вЂЄYou will never. ever break my heart again.

185
00:12:06.875 --> 00:12:09.250
вЂЄMotherfucker.

186
00:12:14.916 --> 00:12:17.125
вЂЄ[hyperventilating]

